      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:121px;">
          <para styleclass="VariableName">You must know : </para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">How to add <text styleclass="Element">Mechanism-Editors</text> to different <text styleclass="Element">Planes</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">The difference between a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Part-Free" styleclass="Element">Free-Part</link> and a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Part-Free" styleclass="Element">Completely Free Part</link>.</para>
        </td>
